page.title: Jabil Circuit Posts Higher Profit
page.text: SAN FRANCISCO (Reuters) - Contract electronics manufacturer Jabil Circuit Inc. <A HREF="http://www.investor.reuters.com/FullQuote.aspx?ticker=JBL.N target=/stocks/quickinfo/fullquote">JBL.N</A> on Tuesday posted a higher quarterly profit on stronger demand for computers, cellphones and other electronic products.
